<c74object name='sp.sinusoidplayer~' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Oscillator bank for the playback of sinusoidal analysis
</digest>
    <description>Oscillator bank for the playback of sinusoidal analysis.
</description>
    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.sinusoidplayer~</o> object is an oscillator bank for the playback of analyzed sinusoidal components. Allows for random variation in envelope parameters so each individual oscillator has its own unique decay.
</discussion>

